{"tid":1083481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【股神看蘋果】畢菲特手機寧用三星摺機 批Apple TV+難突圍","createTime":"2019-03-29T15:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T17:11:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e3366019a9e9d014a5c88aa961425ec6dc846f5","tid":1083481,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553839267_c613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553839267_c613.jpg&h=d99b39da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畢菲特再次展示其使用的手機，為一部價值20美元的Samsung摺機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553837699_af6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553837699_af6d.jpg&h=05edbacb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畢菲特批Apple TV+面對強勁對手，難突圍。<br />\n巴郡（Berkshire Hathaway）持有5.5%蘋果（AAPL）股權，是旗下最大筆的投資項目，不過創辦人畢菲特卻沒有以行動支持蘋果，在昨日（28日）公開的訪問午餐會上，他再次展示其目前使用的手機，是一部價值20美元的舊款摺機，而且更是蘋果競爭對手Samsung，型號SCH-U320。<br />\n<br />\n畢菲特沒給面子使用iPhone，但都會用iPad查看股票行情。他曾表示有老朋友送了一部iPhone X給他，只是他還沒下定決心為手機設定。<br />\n<br />\n股神接受CNBC訪問，主持問他對蘋果兩日前發佈一系列新的訂購服務，包括新聞及娛樂的看法。畢菲特指蘋果進入一個競爭異常激烈的市場，每人只有一雙眼及24小時，市場需求是固定的，蘋果打入娛樂市場就要面對很多聰明的巨大競爭對手，包括過去十年打破行業傳統的Netflix、人人愛看的奧運等體育比賽。他坦言，自己就不會進入一個如此激烈的市場。<br />\n不過，他強調這新方向不會影響其投資取態，因為巴群對蘋果的興趣不是因為其短期財務狀況，而是基於其強大的品牌和生態系統，蘋果在發展娛樂在內的新市場，是可承受一兩個錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190329/59425714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59425714&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7f3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=def4bfc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59425714&h=e5ac4340\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190329/59425714</a><br />\n<br />\n條友又倒自己米<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdb1f21fc09123284c15419f29f36f10b0c2081","tid":1083481,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"以為咁快有Galaxy Fold用"},{"pid":"b107314beea6339766a0fb0d1d0d6f730ba75bff","tid":1083481,"uid":77569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c85d89fab165267ef870811f43dc66e9eb178ba","tid":1083481,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"老人家通常鍾意用實體鍵大字電話"},{"pid":"42612326a994ad964374c0829a10c434777d1021","tid":1083481,"uid":204672,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗做畢彼特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2172c632177c17354ec51aa7d5ac46e11e520e","tid":1083481,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"講左好多次條老野根本唔識it"},{"pid":"863d2382f3e0faad04c96654375e5340d97cae98","tid":1083481,"uid":93649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"de2172c632177c17354ec51aa7d5ac46e11e520e","tid":1083481,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"講左好多次條老野根本唔識it"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"條老野唔識唔緊要<br />\n佢樓下大把分析師同資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e4f9bb75c490ecf8180883963b78aec507056a","tid":1083481,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"個款唔係nokia機咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}